 ITZY 的 Lia 因“极度焦虑”而暂停演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/itzy-lia-hiatus-over-extreme-levels-of-anxiety-3499414?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=itzy-lia-hiatus-over-extreme-levels-焦虑Puah ZiweiMon, 18 Sep 2023 03:55:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3499414 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利亚伊齐中断" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该厂牌补充说，这一决定是在与乐队成员讨论后做出的</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/itzy-lia-hiatus-over-extreme-levels-of-anxiety-3499414">ITZY 的 Lia 因“极度焦虑”而暂停的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利亚伊齐中断" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lia-itzy-hiatus-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>韩国流行女子组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/itzy">ITZY</a>的韩国歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lia">Lia</a>将暂停组合和活动。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/itzy-kill-my-doubt-cake-interview-3475493">ITZY 谈“消除我的怀疑”：“在尝试新事物之前，你总是会有怀疑，对吧？”</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（9月18日），JYP娱乐公司​​宣布，出于对ITZY成员健康的担忧，Lia将退出所有预定的活动。</p><p>这家<a href="https://www.koreaboo.com/news/itzy-lia-take-hiatus-due-health-concerns/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>韩国</em></a>流行音乐经纪公司<a href="https://fans.jype.com/BoardView?BoardName=itzy_NOTICE&amp;Num=900&amp;DivisionId=&amp;SearchField=&amp;SearchQuery=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在一份声明中</a>表示，这位歌手目前“对她的日程安排感到极度紧张和焦虑”。</p><p> JYP娱乐补充说：“她已经接受了医疗咨询和检查，医务人员表示她需要稳定和治疗。” “莉亚暂时不会参加行程，以便专注于治疗。”</p><p>该厂牌补充说，Lia 休息的决定是在与 ITZY 成员讨论后做出的。声明称：“Lia恢复活动的时间将在与她和成员们充分讨论后决定。”</p><p>与此同时，Lia 在 ITZY 的 Instagram 官方账户上手写信件来解决她的中断问题。 “自从我开始这段旅程以来已经六年了……虽然那是一段非常宝贵的时光，但我开始意识到我已经逐渐迷失了自己，”这位歌手写道，由<a href="https://www.soompi.com/article/1614510wpp/itzys-lia-announces-temporary-hiatus-for-health-reasons-shares-handwritten-letter-to-fans" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Soompi</em></a>翻译。</p><p> “我觉得我需要先休息一段时间来爱和充实自己，”她补充道。 “我会努力以健康的状态回归，以报答MIDZY（ITZY的粉丝们）对我的等待和担心。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxUTsQVS6ig/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justif